<section id="about">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>Hello! My name is Rafael Gilberto Chavez Castro, and I am an international student from El Salvador, a country located in Central America. I arrived in Australia in 2022 to pursue a degree in Graphic Design. I have successfully completed Certificates III and IV, as well as a Diploma in Graphic Design at North Metropolitan TAFE. </p>

<p>However, I discovered that Graphic Design was not in high demand as it once was, so I decided to shift my studies to a field with better opportunities for success in Australia: Information Technology. Regardless, I decided to create this professional online portfolio to showcase all my graphic design projects on this portfolio website.</p>

<p>I can offer skills in attention to detail, customer service, and creative thinking. I'm a friendly, hard-working, and reliable person who's willing to learn and gain as much experience as possible. I'm also capable of keeping a long-term position and am skilled in working under pressure and adapting to new situations and challenges to best enhance the organizational brand. </p>

</section>

